<big><big><big><center>⚠️CONTENT WARNING⚠️</center></big></big></big></div><center>
----
----
This page contains some content that you (the reader) may find sensitive, triggering, or disturbing. Those being: ''implications of self-harm, self-destruction & mutilation, gore, implied, obsession, mind control & objectophilia''<sub>that should be pretty clear</sub>

Objectophilia is a romantic orientation that is characterized by love, attraction, etc. towards inanimate objects.

If you find any of the mentioned content not suitable for you, please click off.
